LinkedIn Mobile : +91-6374164867
Professional Summary
Aspiring Full Stack Web Developer with hands-on experience in building interactive web pages using HTML, CSS,
JavaScript, and React.js. Familiar with backend development using Node.js and MongoDB, with strong academic
exposure to Java programming and Database Management Systems (DBMS). Actively working on real-time projects such
as an online grocery shop and a personal portfolio website. Eager to contribute to real-world development teams while
continuously learning and improving backend and full stack capabilities. A fast learner with strong problem-solving skills
and the ability to work independently or in collaborative environments.
Experience
•Personal Projects / Academic Work Tiruchengode, India (Remote)
Full Stack Web Developer (Trainee) July 2025 – Present
◦Grocery Shop Website : Developed a full-stack grocery shopping website using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React.js for the
frontend, and Node.js with MongoDB for backend. Included features like product listings, customer contact form, and admin
dashboard.
◦Power BI : Developed and implemented a Spotify Dashboard using Power BI to visualize music data and insights.
◦Python + DBMS Academic Projects : Built mini-projects simulating real-time CRUD operations. Designed normalized
database schemas and performed SQL queries using MySQL.
◦Portfolio Website (Ongoing) : Building a personal portfolio using React.js and Tailwind CSS. Includes animated skill
progress bars, project showcase, contact section, and downloadable resume.
Certifications / Personal Projects
•Certifications :
◦NPTEL Certification in Internet of Things (IoT) – Silver + Elite
◦NPTEL Certification in Python Programming
◦Infosys Certification in Python Full Stack Development
◦Infosys Certification in Java with Data Structures
◦Web Development Bootcamp – Coursera
◦MongoDB Basics – Great Learning

listing, contact form, and admin dashboard.

downloadable resume.
◦Airline Reservation System (Java) – Simulates flight booking and management using object-oriented programming in
Java.
◦Hospital Management System (DBMS) – CRUD-based database project implementing hospital records using MySQL
and basic UI.
Education
